signature_matches.name: delay execution
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: delay execution
    authors:
      - michael.hunhoff@mandiant.com
      - "@ramen0x3f"
    lib: true
    scope: basic block
    mbc:
      - Anti-Behavioral Analysis::Dynamic Analysis Evasion::Delayed Execution [B0003.003]
    references:
      - https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/sync/wait-functions
      - https://github.com/LordNoteworthy/al-khaser/blob/master/al-khaser/TimingAttacks/timing.cpp
    examples:
      - al-khaser_x86.exe_:0x449770
      - B5F85C26D7AA5A1FB4AF5821B6B5AB9B:0x402FA6
  features:
    - or:
      - and:
        - os: windows
        - or:
          - api: kernel32.Sleep
          - api: kernel32.SleepEx
          - api: kernel32.WaitForSingleObject
          - api: kernel32.SignalObjectAndWait
          - api: kernel32.WaitForSingleObjectEx
          - api: kernel32.WaitForMultipleObjects
          - api: kernel32.WaitForMultipleObjectsEx
          - api: kernel32.RegisterWaitForSingleObject
          - api: WaitOnAddress
          - api: user32.MsgWaitForMultipleObjects
          - api: user32.MsgWaitForMultipleObjectsEx
          - api: NtDelayExecution
          - api: KeWaitForSingleObject
          - api: KeDelayExecutionThread
      - and:
        - os: linux
        - or:
          - api: sleep
          - api: usleep

rule:

signature_matches.name: get OS version
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: get OS version
    authors:
      - "@mr-tz"
    lib: true
    scope: function
    examples:
      - 493167E85E45363D09495D0841C30648:0x401000
      - 5f66b82558ca92e54e77f216ef4c066c:0x44580A
  features:
    - or:
      - api: RtlGetVersion
      - api: ntoskrnl.PsGetVersion
      - api: GetVersion
      - api: GetVersionEx
      - api: VerifyVersionInfo
      - api: VerSetConditionMask
      - api: RtlGetNtVersionNumbers
      - api: GetProductInfo
      - and:
        - match: PEB access
        - or:
          - and:
            - arch: i386
            - or:
              - offset: 0xA4 = PEB->OSMajorVersion
              - offset: 0xA8 = PEB->OSMinorVersion
              - offset: 0xAC = PEB->OSBuildNumber
          - and:
            - arch: amd64
            - or:
              - offset: 0x118 = PEB->OSMajorVersion
              - offset: 0x11C = PEB->OSMinorVersion
              - offset: 0x120 = PEB->OSBuildNumber

signature_matches.name: link many functions at runtime
signature_matches.description: linking/runtime-linking
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: link many functions at runtime
    namespace: linking/runtime-linking
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com
      - joakim@intezer.com
    scope: function
    att&ck:
      - Execution::Shared Modules [T1129]
    examples:
      - b7b5e1253710d8927cbe07d52d2d2e10:0x401000
  features:
    - or:
      - and:
        - os: windows
        - match: link function at runtime on Windows
        - or:
          - count(api(kernel32.GetProcAddress)): 5 or more
          - count(api(ntdll.LdrGetProcedureAddress)): 5 or more
      - and:
        - os: linux
        - match: link function at runtime on Linux
        - or:
          - count(api(dlsym)): 5 or more
          - count(api(dlvsym)): 5 or more

signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:

    namespace: host-interaction/process/terminate
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com

    scope: function
    mbc:

    examples:
      - C91887D861D9BD4A5872249B641BC9F9:0x401A77
      - 9B7CCAA2AE6A5B96E3110EBCBC4311F6:0x10010307

      - api: System.Environment::Exit
      - api: System.Windows.Forms.Application::Exit
      - and:

        - or:
          - api: kernel32.TerminateProcess
          - api: ntdll.NtTerminateProcess
          - api: kernel32.ExitProcess
